headline: Welltower Announces Date of Second Quarter 2025 Earnings Release, Conference Call and Webcast
summary: Welltower® Inc. (NYSE: WELL) today announced it will release second quarter 2025 financial results after the close of trading on the New York Stock Exchange on Monday, July 28, 2025. The Company will host a conference call and webcast on Tuesday, July 29, 2025, at 9:00 a.m. ET to discuss these results. The Company's earnings release will be available in the Investor Relations section of the Company's website.
